The straightforward} 9. Bf4 d6 10. Be2 {cannot be recommended as provoking ...
e6-e5 isn't a real achievement for White:} e5 11. Bg5 h6 12. Bxf6 Qxf6 13. Bg4
Ne7 $15 {Eigminas,K - Teclaf,P Bialystok 2019}) 9... d6 10. Be3 ({White might
