} 10. Kh1 {with an intention to play f2-f4} Ne5 11. Qg3 Nxd3 12. cxd3 d5 $1
$146 ({Worse is} 12... Qg6 {Ginzburg,M - Kovalev,A Saint Vincent 2005} {
in view of} 13. Qd6 $1 Bb8 14. Qa3 $36) 13. exd5 Nxd5 14. Nxd5 exd5 {Black is
close for completing development, and White cannot do much:} 15. Bg5 Qg6 16.
Rae1+ Be6 $11) ({The immediate queen's retreat} 10. Qg3 {also shouldn't bother
Black:} Qg6 11. Qh3 {This was Piorun,K - Pantsulaia,L Batumi 2018} {Now the
