2,36,0,2,1,-21,-17,17,17,4,-8,-8,5,4]} 1. e4 c5 2. Nf3 e6 3. d4 cxd4 4. Nxd4 a6
5. Bd3 Bc5 6. Nb3 Ba7 7. Qg4 {This is only White's 4th choice by statistics,
