0-0}) ({Worth attention is} 10. Bd2 $5 O-O 11. O-O-O Qc7 $1 $146 {This is the
most precise way of handling the position.} (11... b5 {, as was played in a
few games before is risky in view of} 12. Bg5 $1 Nh5 13. Qh4 f6 14. Bd2 {
, and Black's kingside feels too exposed.}) 12. Bg5 Ne8 $1 {This retreat looks
