, as in Arakhamia Grant,K - Ambartsumova,K Chess.com INT 2021 meets} Nce7 $1
13. Bxa7 Rxa7 14. Qe3 Nc8 $1 {,and the Na4 is gone.}) 10... Rxa7 11. O-O-O b4
12. Na4 Bd7 13. Qe3 Nf6 {The vulnerable location of Na4 makes White's position
somwhat uncomfortable. Rubinstein,M-Kulczycki,M LSS email 2006}) 8... d6 {
